{"word":"G4940 - συντυγχάνω - syntynchánō - soon-toong-khan'-o - Come at","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντυγχάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syntynchánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-toong-khan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come at</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடச்சேர்"},{"paragraph":"to meet with, come to, (come at) one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5177 - τυγχάνω - tynchánō - toong-khan'-o/5177\">G5177</a>; to <i>chance together</i>, that is, <i>meet</i> with (<i>reach</i>): - come at.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}